window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Snow won’t be the only thing getting blown</p> <p>Bennett</p> <p>After screwing up a recent hit, I’m broke, blacklisted, and no closer to finding my missing sister. I need a distraction.</p> <p>Five days in Alaska isn’t my idea of a retreat. I hate winter, but I hate Catarina Novak more. If I make her as miserable as possible, maybe I can forget how miserable I am.</p> <p>Frustrating Cat is my favorite pastime, but what happens when I discover something I enjoy more?</p> <p>Cat</p> <p>The winter retreat is a chance to forget all my worries, hang out with my best friend, and finally get my first kill.</p> <p>But when Bennett Carter breezes into the log mansion with his stupidly handsome smirk, he makes it his mission to block my every move. Until we get lost in the woods overnight . . .</p> <p>If our friends discover what happened, we’ll never hear the end of it, but how can we stop what we’ve set in motion? And do we even want to?</p> <p>Welcome to the winter retreat, Sinners!</p> <p>Slay Ride is the second book in the TikTok-favorite Slaycation series. Packed with killer banter, wicked humor, dangerously irresistible romance, and fiery enemies to lovers, this trip is to die for.</p> <p>Listen for the ride of your life . . .</p> <p>Tropes:</p> <p>Grumpy x sunshine<br> Forced proximity<br> Touch her and Enemies-to-lovers<br> He falls first<br> Snowed in<br> THE TURKEY (if you forgot about the pineapple)</p> <p>Although this dark rom-com is \"DIET\" Lauren Biel, it still has adult themes. Full list of content warnings on my website. Please listen responsibly!</p>"; 
